		<descript>
			<langdata>eng</langdata>
			<abstract>
Japan Prefecture Economic Census Data, 1995 is a polygon theme representing prefectures (都/道/府/県) in Japan as of 1995. This map is georeferenced to the surface of the earth and fit to World Geodetic System (1984) coordinates. Attribute data include summary results of the 2015 Japanese census questions regarding economic characteristics. The documentation of these variables can be found in the "Economic" sheet tab from the accompanying code book. This dataset is part of Japan 1995 Census collection.
			</abstract>
		</descript>
